{"tid":1364551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗隱世平價街市，買餸攻略","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:15:06.000Z","uid":38833,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"56ee5ce812100ca24236e9a564e488d14ccc388a","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"好多附近嘅居民都會搭巴士/輕鐵/西鐵黎元朗買餸架<br />\n元朗人通常去三個街市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DghL13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DghL13.png&h=1ffc5239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1）合益街市/同益街市</span><br />\n我覺得就係最大最多人去<br />\n留意返係又新街同雞地中間<br />\n可以邊掃街邊買餸，support體力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2）大橋街市</span><br />\n留意返街市上面係政府合處<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3）朗屏街市</span><br />\n有啲朗屏人都會去依邊買餸<br />\n上面有條天橋可以去西鐵站、輕鐵站、元朗廣場、朗屏邨<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論下、share下邊度買餸平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做個精明既消費者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b55fdf97b150d6c572f0b7ca210f4216f98fd20","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"推 好想知道大家平時買開咩餸"},{"pid":"bfadd3b21574cf38e48a1c5ee93e3362bae00110","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔該大家推推佢<br />\n比啲師奶睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150ca41c252c778b54884b62ce313e7e5c709e68","tid":1364551,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dba2f58aac3a2dd29cedab583bcae6b45a413c0","tid":1364551,"uid":216789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"799ee5d11891006d007eae8ba7c92f033eaef15a","tid":1364551,"uid":188688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"有親戚住荃灣都日日直入元朗買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297731e6e15ef0074e649c58c533967c7d701c63","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"799ee5d11891006d007eae8ba7c92f033eaef15a","tid":1364551,"uid":188688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"有親戚住荃灣都日日直入元朗買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔通元朗街市真係平咁多？計埋車錢時間都要入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf5432c96461bf4d129717bd1b0665c32122ff9","tid":1364551,"uid":188688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"297731e6e15ef0074e649c58c533967c7d701c63","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"799ee5d11891006d007eae8ba7c92f033eaef15a","tid":1364551,"uid":188688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"有親戚住荃灣都日日直入元朗買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔通元朗街市真係平咁多？計埋車錢時間都要入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"2蚊咋嘛車錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老人家唔入嚟飲茶買餸真係嘥晒"},{"pid":"63d8e0dfeae751d4ffc771a3eeba3bce0ecfde81","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cf5432c96461bf4d129717bd1b0665c32122ff9","tid":1364551,"uid":188688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"297731e6e15ef0074e649c58c533967c7d701c63","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"799ee5d11891006d007eae8ba7c92f033eaef15a","tid":1364551,"uid":188688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"有親戚住荃灣都日日直入元朗買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔通元朗街市真係平咁多？計埋車錢時間都要入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"2蚊咋嘛車錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老人家唔入嚟飲茶買餸真係嘥晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"失敬失敬 原來係銀發族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 希望個日多啲人黎元朗飲茶買餸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6324fc9f506e29d90b6c983766dd24ba3d97f2","tid":1364551,"uid":270832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"如果只係諗住行、去觀光，一定要有：<br />\n-背囊<br />\n-為咗環保，要自備硬淨襟用嘅金屬保暖壺、飯壺<br />\n-足夠散銀硬幣，方便找贖、搭車<br />\n-記住拎鎖匙<br />\n-雨遮<br />\n-硬嘢盡量放背囊外，以免頂住自己背部唔舒服，另外最好加啲軟嘢(如浮板，吹氣墊)靠背好啲<br />\n-咁樣執個背囊，就唔怕「銀」住自己唔舒服<br />\n-如果人多擠迫，記得放個背囊落地，唔好向住人、頂住人，整親人就唔好啦。<br />\n-最重要係跟實其他團友，唔好自己走圍行蕩失路。"},{"pid":"6e5fd9196d3e563edcbaee47550faac6faf12608","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家平時唔買開餸既都可以幫屋企買 等屋企人下左淡氣啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啊 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得買多啲雞蛋</span></span></strong> 雞蛋含有豐富既蛋白質 個個人都好需要架！"},{"pid":"0f87221c77debb3cab7f2cfb1aaffe6dab4c7663","tid":1364551,"uid":176657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"星期六可以入元朗幫媽咪買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc20b2ad46b8c290991f80ebb1d179c62ba283a5","tid":1364551,"uid":19337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"我鍾意食雞蛋，要買大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98e8c0334994a96e5f2cc290ea2a4e335ecde45","tid":1364551,"uid":19337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"元朗街市啲紅蘿蔔，青瓜，榴連，菠蘿，正唔正？"},{"pid":"1ca5f4c2a54dc41f7b8a2ca11120f4909fb31b19","tid":1364551,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"大橋街市，買餸順便去神房或者食企鵝"},{"pid":"78c1ef9d572ffa7176594ce6960e1312328f565e","tid":1364551,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f87221c77debb3cab7f2cfb1aaffe6dab4c7663","tid":1364551,"uid":176657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"星期六可以入元朗幫媽咪買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"同媽咪大和解<img src=\"/asset